      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 06:37:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行穆勒称市场押注上半年降息为时尚早</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/ecb-s-muller-says-market-bets-on-first-half-rate-cuts-premature</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员马迪斯·穆勒表示，市场押注欧洲央行将在明年上半年开始降息，这一点有些言过其实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/ecb-s-muller-says-market-bets-on-first-half-rate-cuts-premature</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 06:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在枢纽推动下，香港考虑增加数字绿色债券销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/hong-kong-hires-banks-for-digital-green-bonds-issuance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港正在考虑发行采用分布式账本技术管理的绿色债券，这是香港继今年早些时候首次销售类似债券后，努力成为数字资产中心的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/hong-kong-hires-banks-for-digital-green-bonds-issuance</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 04:08:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的政策组合给投资者带来市场反弹的希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-expands-cash-coffers-with-13th-consecutive-loan-injection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国向经济注入创纪录数量的现金的同时，也对房地产行业重新提供了支持，在零敲碎打的做法让投资者感到沮丧之后，向投资者发出了更强有力的刺激信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/china-expands-cash-coffers-with-13th-consecutive-loan-injection</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 01:24:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储救助集会，油价将自 10 月份以来首次周度上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储的鸽派信号在整个市场释放看涨脉冲后，石油有望在近两个月内首次实现每周上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 00:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美国国债小幅走低，亚洲股市上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市走高，因为投资者仍然相信美联储发出的最明确的信号表明降息即将到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 23:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
